---
import CustomImage from '@/components/CustomImage'
import ImageCarousel from '@/components/ImageCarousel'
import CardCarousel from '@/components/CardCarousel'
import StickyHeader from '@/components/StickyHeader'
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout'

const SITE_TITLE = 'Solstice'
---

<BaseLayout title={SITE_TITLE}>
	<StickyHeader
		title='Solstice'
		buyUrl='https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=2905895118'
		buyLabel='Subscribe on the Workshop'
		exploreLabel='Tech Specs'
		exploreUrl='#specs'
	/>
	<div>
		<h1 class='title text-6xl font-bold'>{SITE_TITLE}</h1>
		<h2 class='text-3xl font-medium mt-4 mb-10'>Reinventing. Reenlightening</h2>
		<CustomImage
			imagePath='/src/assets/images/stormworks/solstice/hero.jpg'
			altText='Reinventing. Reenlightening'
		/>
		<div class='flex justify-center mt-10'>
			<div
				class='w-fit px-4 py-1.5 text-sm rounded-full bg-sky-500 hover:bg-sky-600 text-white font-medium transition-colors'
			>
				<a href='https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=2905895118' target='_blank'
					>Subscribe on the Workshop</a
				>
			</div>
		</div>

		<article class='prose prose-xl dark:prose-invert w-full max-w-none mt-8'>
			<h2>Design</h2>
			<p>
				Solstice is our most popular vehicle ever, and we wanted to improve upon it in every way. So
				we did. This new Solstice has our most advanced control and handling systems we've ever
				built, and some of the most advanced ever built in the game. We've supercharged the engine,
				gave it a new, updated version of our advanced RECO ECU, a higher top speed, new steering,
				advanced entertainment in the back, and so much more.
			</p>
			<CustomImage
				imagePath='/src/assets/images/stormworks/solstice/rear.jpg'
				altText='The new Solstice, with a sleek and modern design, and a powerful new engine'
			/>
			<p>
				New exterior changes including a new third brake light, front light bar, and new side
				indicators all make the car both safer and more realistic.
			</p>

			<h3>Interior</h3>
			<p>
				SenCar 5 takes up the entire dashboard, with all of its wonderful features. New RGB lights
				have been added to give a warmer enterance, feeling more welcoming than ever. Flappy Bird
				has been added for entertainment to the back seat passengers. And new coloring to the
				interior feels better than ever.
			</p>
			<CustomImage
				imagePath='/src/assets/images/stormworks/solstice/int.jpg'
				altText='The interior of the new Solstice, featuring SenCar 5 and new RGB lighting'
			/>

			<h2>SenCar 5</h2>
			<p>
				SenCar 5 is the successor to the powerful car operating system, SenTOS Car 4. SenCar 5
				enhances your car with all new personalization features, seemless communication menthods, a
				brand new UI, drive modes, and more. SenCar 5 features a brand new UI, made from scratch,
				with as little compromises as possible. There are 4 new screens, 2 are optional, for a full
				new experience of using SenCar 5, and any car it is in. SenCar 5 is designed to take over
				nearly every element of a car, and the 4 new screens let you control them perfectly. Built
				on top of the powerful SenOS architecture, it is easier than ever to control a car now.
			</p>
			<CustomImage
				imagePath='/src/assets/images/stormworks/solstice/dash.jpg'
				altText='The new SenCar 5 dashboard of the new Solstice, with all new features and a brand new UI'
			/>
			<p>
				SenCar 5 features 7 themes to customize your experience with the car to the max. Custom
				currated colors match each theme perfectly, so that they dont contrast eachother.
			</p>
			<br />
			<CustomImage
				imagePath='/src/assets/images/stormworks/solstice/eng.jpg'
				altText='Solstice has a fuel efficient V4 engine powering it'
			/>

			<h2>So much more</h2>
			<ul>
				<li>Horn</li>
				<li>Downshift protection</li>
				<li>Shows open doors on dashboard</li>
				<li>Enhanced trip stats</li>
				<li>Low fuel/battery alarms</li>
				<li>Enhanced clutch</li>
				<li>Developer support</li>
				<li>Open source</li>
				<li>More settings</li>
				<li>More "on-the-fly" settings</li>
			</ul>

			<p>
				<a
					href='https://github.com/SentyFunBall/SW-SenCar-5'
					target='_blank'
					rel='noreferrer'
					class='underline text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700 dark:text-blue-400 dark:hover:text-blue-300'
					>SenCar 5 Source Code & Dev updates</a
				>
			</p>
			<p>
				<a
					href='https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-_KnjahEiBI'
					target='_blank'
					rel='noreferrer'
					class='underline text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700 dark:text-blue-400 dark:hover:text-blue-300'
					>Watch the trailer on YouTube</a
				>
			</p>

			<h2 id='specs'>Specs</h2>
			<ul>
				<li>4 cylinder (L Config) supercharged modular engine</li>
				<li>5 speed AutoManual transmission</li>
				<li>SenCar 5 with SIBTaT</li>
				<li>RECO 1.3</li>
				<li>Top speed: 140mph/225kph</li>
			</ul>

			<h2>Micros used</h2>
			<ul>
				<li>SenCar v5.0</li>
				<li>Custom SIBTaT Controller</li>
				<li>RECO v1.3</li>
			</ul>
		</article>
	</div>
</BaseLayout>

<script>
	import { animate } from 'motion'
	const showAnimations = localStorage.getItem('animations') === 'true'

	if (showAnimations) {
		animate(
			'.title',
			{ y: [80, 0], opacity: [0, 1] },
			{
				duration: 2.5,
				opacity: { duration: 3 },

				offset: [0, 0.55, 0.75]
			}
		)
	}
</script>
